title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ on This Week’s FIB Priority File
content:
Former FIB agent Jodi Marshall is on the hunt for a vital recording device stashed aboard a hijacked jet in The Black Box File. Garment Factory owners can take on this week’s multi-stage FIB Priority File and secure 2X GTA$ on top of its already boosted payout.

FIB Priority Files can only be completed once each week. Look for the Priority File tag when using the Darnell Inc. App on your iFruit.
